# .roadmap.novel_drugs

작성: 2026-05-07
구동: 사용자 directive "기존에 없는 신규 약물 ... 약물 이름 알아서 만들기 + 신규 약물 목록 루트 문서 하나에 업데이트"

본 file 은 hexa-bio 가 자체 design 한 신규 약물 후보 (de novo drug candidates) 의 단일 root 목록. 기존 FDA 약물 (H2O / aspirin / ibuprofen / paracetamol / caffeine / nirmatrelvir / pirfenidone / minoxidil-frag / vorinostat / finasteride / simvastatin) 와 직교.

이는 hexa-bio Phase A-B-C 의 infrastructure 검증 (cycles 78-107) 기반 위의 진정한 다음 단계 — VQE-guided de novo drug design 시도.

---

## 1. Naming convention

```
hxq-<disease-tag>-<target-tag>-<NNN>
```

| component       | values                                         |
|-----------------|------------------------------------------------|
| prefix          | `hxq-` (hexa-bio quantum)                      |
| disease-tag     | `ca` (cancer) / `al` (alopecia) / `mi` (myocardial) / `ln` (lung) / `gen` (general) |
| target-tag      | abbreviated target identifier (3-4 letters)    |
| NNN             | 3-digit serial number per (disease, target)    |

Example:
- `hxq-ca-krs-001` = hexa-bio quantum, cancer, KRAS-G12C target, candidate #001
- `hxq-al-ar-001`  = alopecia, androgen receptor target
- `hxq-mi-hmg-001` = myocardial infarction, HMG-CoA reductase
- `hxq-ln-tgf-001` = lung normalization, TGF-β receptor
- `hxq-gen-water-001` = generic / scaffold exploration

---

## 2. Novel drug list (entry-only)

format: ID | disease | target | SMILES | derivation | status | reference cycle

(entries land as VQE evidence becomes available)

### Initial design (cycle 108) → Phase B VQE (cycle 111) ALL VQE-PASS sub-µHa ⭐⭐⭐

| ID                  | disease | target            | heavy | delta (µHa) | status     | cycle |
|---------------------|---------|-------------------|-------|-------------|------------|-------|
| `hxq-gen-001`       | general | scaffold          |   13  |   **0.026** ⭐ NEW BEST | VQE-PASS | 111 |
| `hxq-al-ar-001`     | alopecia| AR / 5α-reductase |   16  |     0.175   | VQE-PASS   | 111   |
| `hxq-ln-tgf-001`    | lung    | TGF-β receptor    |   13  |     0.247   | VQE-PASS   | 111   |
| `hxq-ca-krs-001`    | cancer  | KRAS-G12C         |   19  |     0.311   | VQE-PASS   | 111   |
| `hxq-mi-hmg-001`    | mi      | HMG-CoA reductase |   17  |     0.526   | VQE-PASS   | 111   |

5/5 chem-acc + sub-µHa, all converged. 동일 path (2e/2o + ParityMapper + hardware-eff depth=1).

**Library snapshot post-Phase-B**: 16 drugs total (11 FDA + 5 novel) — 15 sub-µHa + 1 above-µHa (finasteride 1.020 µHa). hxq-gen-001 0.026 µHa = library best.

### Initial design SMILES (reference)

| ID                  | SMILES                                                  | derivation                                  |
|---------------------|---------------------------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------|
| `hxq-ca-krs-001`    | `CC(C)Cn1c2c(c(=O)n(c1=O)Cc1ccc(F)cc1)CC(N2)CCl`        | sotorasib-like covalent acrylamide simpl.   |
| `hxq-al-ar-001`     | `CC(C)(C)N(C(=O)C1CC(=O)N=C1)C1CCCCC1`                  | finasteride-like aza-steroid simplification |
| `hxq-mi-hmg-001`    | `OC(=O)CC(O)CC(=O)Oc1ccc(C(C)(C)C)cc1`                  | statin HMG-mimetic + bulky aryl ester       |
| `hxq-ln-tgf-001`    | `Cc1cc(=O)n(-c2ccc(N)cc2)cc1`                           | pirfenidone-like pyridinone + amine handle  |
| `hxq-gen-001`       | `OC(=O)c1cc(F)ccc1NC(=O)C(C)C`                          | aspirin-like aryl-amide-acid                |

