## 3. Status legend

| status        | meaning                                                              |
|---------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------|
| DESIGN        | SMILES specified, no VQE yet                                         |
| BUILD-PASS    | Hamiltonian build PASS via pocket_active_space.py 2e/2o              |
| VQE-PASS      | sub-µHa or chem-acc PASS for isolated molecule (Phase B-real path)   |
| POCKET-VQE    | explicit pocket supersystem VQE PASS (Tier 1 ramp F-Q-6-D)           |
| RANKING-PASS  | library ranking vs known FDA inhibitor with Spearman > 0.8            |
| BLOCKED       | build / VQE / pocket fail with documented reason                     |

